    <sys:String x:Key="LOCSsvMoveFolderExplain" xml:space="preserve">Adds a game menu action to move screenshots from all configured source folders to one archive folder.
The archive folder path uses the destination field above. If {Name} is missing in that path, it is added automatically.
Files are renamed using &quot;File pattern&quot;, then plugin links are updated.

Example:
Source folders:
- {Public}\Screenshots
- {SteamScreenshotsDir}\435790\screenshots

Archive destination:
{DropboxFolder}\Screenshots\{Name}</sys:String>

